wield
Discworld player help
wield

Name
.SI 5
wield - wield weapons.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
wield <item|hands>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Wield lets you wield a weapon.  To use it type wield followed by the weapon you
wish to use, or if you want to stop wielding a weapon, just wield your hands.
.EP

Examples :
.SI 5
wield war hammer
wield second scythe
wield hands
.EP

See also
.SI 5
wear, remove.
.EI
